            </p>
         </note>
         <p xml:id="uuid_f7631a40-c25e-409c-ac41-fe627136d391">
            <lb xml:id="uuid_fdd7e77c-956f-4f55-b081-5e45ce7f541b"/><note resp="law-firm" type="paratext"><rs ref="#pmb11988" type="person">Kraus</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb37568" type="institution">Der Wiener Tag</rs><lb xml:id="uuid_7a41caad-5758-4589-9cf9-28cb8610e6a2"/>exp. 24.12.1930.</note>
         </p>
